commit.message: New modules.alias file with newer hardware support.
Fixed a bug where depgen was trying to remove a line in the PossibleLists object instead of its list of lines.

Merge pull request #5 from ulziibuyan/master

Use UTF-8 on Kconfig files.
Safer file openings and replacing usage of cat with python functions.
Added --default option, and changed --new to use allnoconfig
Different approach of generating file systems
